印象阿里--透过绩效看管理第1讲

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appqn049wAm2506/a_5c89b355e18bf_S4Ya2Bwi

<section style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; padding: 0px 5px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 5px 0px 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程背景</p></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0.5em; height: 1.8em; border-left: 0.9em solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom: 0.9em solid transparent !important; border-top: 0.9em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">所有员工行为的背后，一定有文化的牵引；<br/> 所有团队习惯的背后，一定有文化的默认；<br/> 所有问题表象的背后，一定有文化的偏差。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/> 阿里巴巴对于企业文化的重视可谓到了极致，正如马云所说，“文化是企业发展的DNA，决定着一家公司的性格和命运”。阿里文化从创业之初就启动，一路成长，基于战略发展进行了4次文化调整，在看不见的地方创造更高维度的竞争力。<br/> <br/> </p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">“文化是虚的，必须做实”，虚的一面就是意识形态上的，比如说使命、愿景、价值观、思维方式。而实的一面就是具体行为上的，比如说行为规范、方式方法、制度。文化既是全体员工约法三章的规范，也是上阵打战的信念。文化一旦形成，很难改。一定要找出文化考核的具体办法出来，要和员工的利益相关。不能考核的企业文化全是瞎扯，否则文化就是浪费资源和时间。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; padding: 0px 5px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 5px 0px 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">授课讲师</p></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0.5em; height: 1.8em; border-left: 0.9em solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom: 0.9em solid transparent !important; border-top: 0.9em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appr5MeXbxz2343/image/ueditor/88872800_1552448640.png" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">王建和</strong><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">现任天津商聚电子商务有限公司总经理。商聚旗下有三家子公司，分别涉及跨境B2B贸易，B2C贸易，网络技术服务，软件开发，以及跨境电商产业园。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">阿里9年实战经验，7年管理生涯致力于《向管理要订单》《过程与目标管理》《抓过程 拿结果》《销售铁军团队打造》等。注重团队日常工作，关心团队日常生活，团队管理中刚中有柔柔中带刚，张弛有度地建设完全开放、责任、成长的团队。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; padding: 0px 5px; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 5px 0px 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程收益</p></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0.5em; height: 1.8em; border-left: 0.9em solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom: 0.9em solid transparent !important; border-top: 0.9em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1、学习文化落地成功标杆企业案例——阿里巴巴</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2、系统了解企业文化，认识企业文化长成和演变的全景</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3、深入了解企业文化对于企业发展的意义和重要性</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4、真正了解文化如何激活组织、赋能人才</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">5、清晰文化对于个人的重要性，实现自我认知自我超越</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><sectio